---

# Step 10 Install MAVSDK

```bash
sudo apt install libmavsdk-dev
```

Verify

```bash
pkg-config --modversion mavsdk
```

---

# Step 11 Connect Qt to PX4

Typical connection

```
Qt QML

↓

C++ Backend

↓

MAVSDK

↓

UDP 14540

↓

PX4 SITL

↓

Gazebo
```

PX4 default SITL port

```
udp://:14540
```

