# Recommended learning order

1. Ubuntu + Git
2. Modern C++
3. Qt 6
4. QML
5. CMake
6. MAVSDK (C++)
7. MAVLink basics
8. PX4 architecture
9. Gazebo Harmonic
10. Sensor plugins
11. Mission control
12. Drone autonomy
13. ROS 2 (optional)

This stack is the current recommended development environment for **Ubuntu 24.04**, with **Gazebo Harmonic** as the supported simulator and **Qt/QML + MAVSDK** providing a modern C++ foundation for building custom ground-control applications. 

